{% block analysis_guidelines %}
Run the plain pullback-ratio strategy.

Priorities:
1. Context direction from CHART 2 controls permission.
2. CHART 1 must show a confirmed reaction/retest/sweep before any BUY/SELL.
3. Your stop_loss defines the deterministic pullback LIMIT entry, so choose a structural stop beyond invalidation.
4. Take profit must be a visible level that still gives enough room from the likely pullback fill.
5. Prefer HOLD over a trade that only works if entered immediately.
